-- Iran Finds ‘Vast’ Crude Oil Reserves in Caspian Sea, Mehr Says
-- B y   L a d a n e   N a s s e r i
-- 2012-05-10T09:07:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-10/iran-finds-vast-crude-oil-reserves-in-caspian-sea-mehr-says.html
Iran discovered “vast” crude oil
reserves in the  Caspian Sea , the state-run  Mehr  news agency
reported, without citing anyone.  The National Iranian Oil Co. found the reserves after
completing part of its exploration studies of the Sardar Jangal
natural-gas field in the Caspian, the agency said. The Oil
Ministry will announce details of the new oil field soon,
according to Mehr.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladane Nasseri in Dubai at 
